Oreck Clean Home Center provides a range of vacuum products under the Oreck XL brand. It is one of the stores of Oreck Corporation, which has been operational since 1963. The store offers heavy-duty vacuum cleaners and cleaning products. It also provides air purifiers, vacuum bags, belts, accessories and appliances. Oreck Clean Home Center offers replacement parts and floor care machines. In addition, it provides products under the Oreck XL ProShield brand. The parent company manufactures vacuum cleaners for the hotel industry in the United States. It also sells products in Europe and Asia. Oreck Corporation offers shipping services for products.
